    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily commuting. Mechanically, it is sound and starts reliably, though it shows the expected wear and tear of a car its age. The exterior has some noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior would benefit from a deep clean, but there are no major structural issues. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone looking for transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
