    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs smooth as silk and the interior has been kept nice and tidy. It\u2019s got a little bit of character from the road, but it\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that still turns heads, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
